name: Venus de Milo
comments: Absolutely the best - I saw the Columbus Jazz Orchestra perform all of the Birth of the Cool jazz tracks recently.  These tracks are unbelievably complicated.  Also makes me want to listen to Television.
When you find the girl that loves Miles....marry her. Doesnt get any better.
Even without arms, she's a natural beauty...and this track ain't even half bad, neither.(-;
ESTA É A VENUS DA MUSICA.SIMPLISMENTE DEMAIS!!!
The Venus de Milo is armless and harmless. Last saw her in the Louvre. For real love and beauty, listen to Miles Davis.
pu doo, pu doo, pap pap...
the very best in the world!!!
Black prince. Period the end 57-69 only like me.
Dreamy and delightful. I love Birth of the Cool, so wonderfully arranged, like an intricate jigsaw puzzle that reveals a beautiful series of pictures.
